{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Inquiry into energy companies customer service and Ombudsman\u2019s remit.",
        "additional_details": "The ordinary customer is receiving appalling service at the hands of energy companies who can bill what they like , when they want and refuse to address that they may be at fault . The ombudsman is not fully fit for the purpose and needs more powers of investigation and more power to award higher compensation levels.",
        "background": "Establish an enquiry into energy companies service and the redress that is available to the ordinary customer. At present the power is totally with the energy companies who operate a war of attrition against their customers. The ombudsman\u2019s remit should be changed so they have more powers.",
